  "curation": {
    "synopsis": "Jarene and the Wild Cats are House Escher fighters in Hive Primus, until an ambush leaves a Guilder and their own leader dead and turns the whole crew into outlawed prey. Hunted by Enforcers, guilders, rival Houses and bounty-hungry gangs, Jarene has to keep her sisters alive long enough to prove the killing was a set-up. Mike Brooks frames the chase as Underhive noir: a hunted-gang procedural about Escher loyalty, street justice and survival when Necromunda decides your name is worth more as a corpse.",
